    <!-------------------------- Outcomes ---------------------------->

    <div class="container pb-5 w-60">
      <h3 class="pt-5 my-5 text-center font-weight-bold">Outcomes</h3>
      <p>The updated design was well received within Tete-A-Tete company. While it has not been published yet it has already increased
        communication within the company and inspired stylists to document their best works in order to showcase their skills and expertise.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="container my-5 w-60">
      <h3 class="text-center my-5 font-weight-bold">Next steps and recommendations:</h3>
      <div class="container w-75">
        <ul>
          <li>Keep up to date online appearance on the social networks such as Instagram and Facebook.</li>
          <li>Add online booking feature.</li>
          <li>Launch new marketing campaigns via Constant Contact.</li>
